    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Honestly, I'm a little sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new adventure. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been totally babied since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and it's basically spotless inside and out. If you've been looking for that perfect, like-new ride without the brand-new price tag, you've found it! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
