    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. Beneath the hood, the S54B32 power plant features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally flawless, having received proactive subframe reinforcement and a documented rod bearing replacement. Power is managed via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional lateral grip and exit speeds. The factory finish is impeccable, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero mechanical deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
