    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in breathtaking, showroom-ready condition. Meticulously maintained by a single owner and kept in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior paint retains its deep, factory-fresh luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, reflecting a life of pampered care. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery still carries that new-car scent and shows no signs of wear, while the dashboard and trim are entirely free of sun damage or scratches. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history with every scheduled maintenance performed exclusively at the authorized dealership. It drives with the tightness, silence, and precision of a brand-new vehicle. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been treated as a prized possession since day one. The sale includes all original manuals, a complete set of service records, two sets of keys, and the original window sticker.",
